<p>As the leadign provider of XML
infrastructure for the B2B market,
Bowstreet is at the vanguard of there</br>
e-commerce revolution.
Central the its vision is technology
known as the Business Web
Factory, which enables line-of-business
managers to create
instant B2B web relationships that
can be massively customized.

<p><font class="sectionTitleText">Requirements</font>

<p>The viability
of the Business Web Factory
relies on the ability of Bowstreet,
together with its customers and
partners, to extend BWF's core
capabilities with technology components
called "builders." With
these enhancements, users can
create web services of unbounded
sophistication.

<p><font class="sectionTitleText">Nevo's Solution</font>

<p>In light of
our proven ability to master and
deliver new technologies and
architectures, Bowstreet turned
to Nevo as the first outside development
orgaization capable of
creating these new components.
In addition, Nevo was able to
capture the learning process and
provide complete documentation
that help Bowstreet rapidly
expand its partner community.
This collaboration was so successful
that Bowstreet and Nevo
have entered into an alliance in
which Nevo provides development
services not only to Bowstreet,
but also to other organizations
seeking to utilize Bowstreet's
products and services.


